Beverly Hills Pawn, Season 2, Episode 12.

First aired on February 12, 2014.


"The Dude and The Dancer" - A piece from 'The Big Lebowski'; a customer looks to purchase a mangalore head from 'The Fifth Element'; Yossi and Cori make a trip to their client's home to see a Degas piece; a prop from 'Beautiful Creatures.'
